					<span style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:#D4CABE;display:block;margin-bottom:3px;">Accessibility bar</span>
					<span style="font-size:13px;color:#D4CABE;">A real ARIA slider role, arrow-key operable, never a bare draggable div.</span>
				</div>
